.page-header
  h1#donations Donations

p
  | This project is funded through donations.  If you find
  | CAMotics useful please consider donating $25 or more.
  | Your donations will make new features, bug fixes
  | and the continued development of this software possible.

h3 Make a One-time Donation
p
  | To make a <b>one-time</b> donation with Paypal click the graphic below:

  form(action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post")
    input(name="cmd" value="_s-xclick" type="hidden")
    input(name="hosted_button_id" value="FDP4SVEVT68NG" type="hidden")
    input.donate-button(src="images/donate.png" name="submit" type="image")

h3 Make a Recurring Donation
p
  | Want to really help this project?  Make a recurring donation:

  form(action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post")
    input(type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick")
    input(type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="V8RMSHW39GTMY")
    input(type="hidden" name="currency_code" value="USD")
    select(name="os0")
      option(value="Advocate" selected) Advocate : $5.00 USD - monthly
      option(value="Supporter" selected) Supporter : $10.00 USD - monthly
      option(value="Generous") Generous : $25.00 USD - monthly
      option(value="Philanthropist") Philanthropist : $50.00 USD - monthly
      option(value="Boss") The Boss : $100.00 USD - monthly
    input(type="submit" name="submit" value="Make a recurring donation")

